Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.53,0:00:04.47,Default@HKG,,0000,0000,0000,,滿月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:07.87,Default@HKG,,0000,0000,0000,,儀式之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:10.24,Default@HKG,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說時機已經成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:15.10,Default@HKG,,0000,0000,0000,,但依舊缺少一個來主持儀式的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:19.48,Default@HKG,,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此 我們也別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.64,Default@HKG,,0000,0000,0000,,日期滿了 神的國近了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:29.61,Default@HKG,,0000,0000,0000,,Quoniam impletum est tempus,et appropinquavit regnum Dei:poenitemini,et credite Evangelio
